# Laravel i18n

- Use English source strings in `__()` calls inside Blade views.
- Keep Vietnamese translations in `app/lang/vi.json`; update it whenever adding, changing, or removing a visible English key.
- Do not add new Vietnamese source strings like `__('Đăng nhập')`; use `__('Log in')` with a `vi.json` entry instead.
- Preserve Laravel placeholders exactly, e.g. `:time`, `:name`.
